<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>蛋糕目錄 - 祥盛中西禮餅</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/logo.png">
</head>

